title: G-SHOCK X COMPLEX Watch Lookbook - Season of the Light
description: You can feel it coming. The chill. The crispness in the air. The darkness. But winter does not have to be a dark time, nor a cold time. Winter can be full of brightness, life, and light. G-SHOCK is proud to introduce six new collections that defy the cold, defy the dark, and—most importantly—defy expectations.
